title: FANTASTIC FOUR (Marvel NOW) 001-009 (Up-to-date through June 19,
description:
We have seen the future and it will be fantastic! When Reed and Sue decide that the family needs to relax, they take Ben, Johnny and the kids on a little vacation... through all of infinite time and space!

------

This is an outstanding Marvel NOW relaunch of the classic series that sparked the Marvel Age of Comics 52 years ago. Reed gets bitten by a dinosaur (is that you, Devil Dinosaur?) and realizes his flesh is starting to decay... He takes his family on an educational space-time vacation, all the while hoping to find a cure. Guest-starring Julius Caesar, Blastaar, and at least a dozen Dr. Dooms! Give it a try, if you haven't been following it.  --STF
